				<td colspan="2"><span>Speed of the mob also plays a factor Velvett.Where are you kiting? Run speed should be capped with TDoK. PoV mobs are different than HoH mobs. Do not know about PoN mobs yet, I haven't tried them but have seen them done. You can also go too fast. It takes time and testing to get it right in any zone you try. If it is starting out ok, but you get hit over time, use ctrl to tighten them up a bit.A tap here and there helps, got to be careful with it tho. DA as autocircle is started helps tighten them up also. Just run into them. Don't add lightcrawlers in PoV(hitbox too big), or white suit guys in HoH, they summon. Other than that, good hunting:)</span></td>
